A few reminders on this sunny Friday, August 22nd:
1.  To ticketholders...  Tomorrow, the SOCIAL CLUB TAIL GATE POT LUCK, with fun & games gets underway at 5:00 pm! Don't forget to wear your favorite team shirt or, go the extra mile for a chance to win the 'Best Dressed Crazy Sports Fan Contest!"
2.  The Big Red Bus will be in the Clubhouse parking lot for their quarterly BLOOD DRIVE on Monday, August 25th from 1:00 pm - 6:00 pm.  All donors will receive a $20 eGift card, an insulated 'Top Handle' water bottle and wellness check to include blood pressure, iron count and cholesterol screening.
3. To those signed up to join us... We'll see you next Tuesday, August 26th at 1:30 pm for our FREE 'Aberdeen Rocks' painting workshop. All supplies will be provided!
Make it a great weekend!
